00:04:22.410 --> 00:04:25.240
Minus 35 meters per second, and
then of course, multiply

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:26.600
both sides by negative 1.

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:31.490
And the initial velocity is
equal to 35 meters per second.

00:04:31.490 --> 00:04:32.520
That wasn't too bad.

00:04:32.520 --> 00:04:34.810
You don't even have to really
do it formally like this.

00:04:34.810 --> 00:04:38.720
You could just say well I'm
