00:04:45.060 --> 00:04:50.200
go to 0, and it's decelerating
at this speed, right?

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:54.400
So every second it's getting 10
meters per second slower.

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:56.520
Every second I go,
it's getting 10

00:04:56.520 --> 00:04:58.070
meters per second slower.

00:04:58.070 --> 00:05:04.040
So if it took 3-1/2 seconds to
go to 0, I must have started

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:06.480
